'''Muta''' was a 7th-century [[Daylamites|Daylamite]] king, who fought against the [[Muslim conquest of Persia|Arabs]] in the [[battle of Waj Rudh]]. He was, however, defeated and killed by Nu'aym ibn Muqarrin.

